    "The GLUE-X dataset is comprised of 8 training datasets and 16 evaluation datasets, with all training datasets sourced from GLUE.",
    "It assesses the OOD performance of models across classic NLP tasks, encompassing syntactic judgment, sentiment analysis, semantic matching, textual entailment, and reading comprehension.",
    "• LAiW (Dai et al, 2023).",
    "The LAiW dataset systematically arranges pre-existing legal datasets, dividing assessment tasks into three primary legal competencies, comprising a total of 13 fundamental assignments.",
    "Fundamental tasks in NLP encompass the retrieval of statutes, recognition of elements, identification of named entities, summarization of judicial key points, and the identification of legal cases."
